The paper deals with the problem of detecting references to datasets in social science articles, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and related topics. The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which suggests categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.DL (Digital Libraries). Additionally, the paper deals with machine learning techniques, which suggests categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
